; Regression test for issue #1145: Using 'bucket' bypasses checks/features
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1145
;
; The bucket directive bypassed alias expansion, meaning that
; `bucket AliasName` would create a new account instead of resolving
; the alias to the target account.
;
; Test 1: bucket + strict mode (implicitly declared)
; Test 2: bucket resolves account aliases

account Expenses:Food
account Assets:Bank
    alias Checking
commodity $

bucket Checking

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $50.00

test bal --strict
             $-50.00  Assets:Bank
              $50.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test

test bal Assets:Bank
             $-50.00  Assets:Bank
end test
